query:
SELECT 
  id,
  addressLine1,
  city,
  state,
  buildingSquareFeet,
  totalBedrooms,
  totalBaths,
  yearBuilt,
  propertyType,
  estimatedValue,
  equityAmount,
  equityPercent,
  mortgageAmount,
  totalLoanBalance,
  salePrice,
  saleDate,
  taxAmount,
  taxYear,
  owner1Name
FROM properties 
WHERE id >= 780003 
ORDER BY id 
LIMIT 5;
